This Project has been created to map the Bongo-Project store protocol to a more Ruby - Rails friendly file or gem I don't know.

The Bongo Store Protocol Spec can be found here

http://www.bongo-project.org/Documentation/Store_Protocol

This project is Licensed as follows.

GNU General Public License V2 or later

The Project page is here

http://www.bongo-project.org/Development/RBongo

I would appreciate any help to get this going.